title: AutoCad 2009 32bit
description:
Autodesk Auto Cad 2009 (Norske Seedere)

_____________________________________________________________________________________

AutoCAD software lets you design, visualize, and document your ideas clearly and efficiently. With AutoCAD 2009 you wil move to new highs of productivity. New features help conceptualize and visualize designs, accelerate tasks, and allow commands to be easily found.

_____________________________________________________________________________________

AutoCAD System Requirements


32-bit AutoCAD 2009:

    * Intel Pentium 4 processor or AMD Athlon, 2.2 GHz or greater
      or
      Intel or AMD Dual Core processor, 1.6 GHz or greater
    * Microsoft Windows Vista, Window XP SP2 operating systems 

For Microsoft Windows XP SP2:

    * 1 GB RAM
    * 750 MB free disk space for installation
    * 1024x768 VGA with true color
    * Microsoft Internet Explorer 6.0 (SP1 or higher)

__________________________________________________________________________________

1: Mount image: "AUtocad 2009" in PowerIso

2: Open the disk-station in "My Computer"

3: In the "x86" folder run the file: "acad.msi" (In case off error, run the       "setup.exe" file first. Then trye the "acad.msi" again.)

4: Run "ACAD 2009" 

5: Select Activate the Product when ask for activation. Use 666-98989898 as serial.

6: Open the xforce keygen ("xf-acad9-32-BITS.exe") in the Crack folder in the disk-station in "My Computer". 

7: Enter the serial and press generate

8: Copy and paste the activation code.

9: Finaly: restart ACAD 2009.
